The FOTA Manager (FotaMgr) controls the Firmware Over The Air (FOTA) Client on the device, which allows administrators to perform OS updates on Zebra devices without a physical connection. The FOTA Client app comes preinstalled on supported devices and is hard-wired to communicate with the Zebra update server. 

> **Supported only on devices running Android 6.x Marshmallow and later**. 

### Main Functionality

* Set the State (active/inactive) of the FOTA Client on the device 
* Enable/disable the FOTA user interface on the device

